  <brief_title>Glu298Asp Polymorphism and Blood Pressure</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Beetroot Bread on Postprandial Blood Pressure According to Glu298Asp Polymorphism in the eNOS Gene</official_title>
  <sponsors>
